&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are excited to announce that our ASC Team is ready to grow!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking the right candidate to join our team as an ASC Coordinator in a &lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;90-day temporary position, with the potential for permanent employment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; based on ongoing business needs. This is a part-time, remote opportunity to support customer inquiries by phone, email, social media, and online reviews.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate is a strong multitasker with a proven ability to convert inquiries into appointments and provide exceptional customer service across multiple communication channels, including social media comments and reviews.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;Acquisitions Support Center Coordinator:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Acquisitions Support Center Coordinator supports and manages prospect onboarding; from the first point of contact from an inquiry, to their Introductory Session with FastFit or The Perfect Workout.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Acquisitions Support Center Coordinator manages prospect interest communication across multiple channels, with the intent for the inquiry to schedule and show up for an Introductory Session.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Acquisitions Support Center Coordinator oversees social media responses for FastFit and The Perfect Workout, and also develops and implements communication for all inquiries.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Acquisitions Support Center Coordinator is also responsible for managing active member communications with efficient response times to address any customer service needs, issues, questions or concerns.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Finally, the Acquisitions Support Center Coordinator follows procedures and facilitates any communication needed between active members, the studios, and Regional Managers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Functions&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prospect onboarding&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Schedule Introductory Sessions for open inquiries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and implement communication processes for social media inquiries 4. Assist active members with customer service needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate communication between members, inquiries, and company staff&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Description of Duties&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prospect Onboarding&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;○ This process includes receiving prospect outreach by call, text or email, and responding in a timely manner in order to schedule the inquiry for an&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;introductory session with FastFit or The Perfect Workout.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;○ This also includes all prospect communication for social media platforms such as Facebook, Instagram, YouTube, Google and Yelp.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;○ Finally, this process follows procedures and facilitates any communication needed between inquiries, the studios, and Regional Managers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Member Services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;○ This process includes managing active member communications with efficient response times to address any customer service needs, issues, questions or concerns.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;○ Finally, this process follows procedures and facilitates any communication needed between active members, inactive members, the studios, and Regional Managers.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
